==English==

===Noun===
'''arc''' (''plural:'' '''arcs''')

#A curve.
#{{geometry}} A [[circular arc]].
#{{geometry}} A continuous section of any curve.
#{{mathematics}} A [[continuous]] [[mapping]] from the [[real]] [[interval]] <nowiki>[0, 1]</nowiki>.
#{{graphtheory}} A [[directed edge]].

====Synonyms====
*(''curve''): [[curve]], [[swoop]]
*(''circular arc''): [[circular arc]], [[circle segment]]<!--according to the Wikipedia article-->
*(''directed edge''): [[arrow]], [[directed edge]]

